   "end": 767.28,
   "text": "And I just happened to have like $3,000."
  },
  {
   "start": 767.84,
   "end": 768.0,
   "text": "No."
  },
  {
   "start": 768.02,
   "end": 770.1,
   "text": "At the time it was my $50,000 HELOC loan."
  },
  {
   "start": 770.1,
   "end": 773.18,
   "text": "And I just happened to have like $4,000 in it."
  },
  {
   "start": 773.44,
   "end": 774.88,
   "text": "And so I used my HELOC loan."
  },
  {
   "start": 774.88,
   "end": 777.84,
   "text": "To pay this phantom tax they gave me."
  },
  {
   "start": 778.74,
   "end": 780.68,
   "text": "With the other $150 bucks that they're."
  },
  {
   "start": 781.0,
   "end": 781.54,
   "text": "And I looked."
  },
  {
   "start": 781.64,
   "end": 782.18,
   "text": "And I called."
  },
  {
   "start": 782.28,
   "end": 783.72,
   "text": "And this lady was all being a bitch to me."
  },
  {
   "start": 783.78,
   "end": 784.06,
   "text": "And I'm like."
  },
  {
   "start": 784.14,
   "end": 784.94,
   "text": "That nobody ever told me."
  },
  {
   "start": 784.98,
   "end": 785.26,
   "text": "She's like."
  },
  {
   "start": 785.28,
   "end": 786.26,
   "text": "Of course they didn't."
  },
  {
   "start": 787.08,
   "end": 787.7,
   "text": "And like that."
  },
  {
   "start": 787.82,
   "end": 789.18,
   "text": "That was rude as hell."
  },
  {
   "start": 789.3,
   "end": 790.58,
   "text": "But I was like with my mom."
  },
  {
   "start": 790.72,
   "end": 790.8,
   "text": "So."
  },
  {
   "start": 791.5,
   "end": 792.4,
   "text": "At my mom's house."
  },
  {
   "start": 792.5,
   "end": 792.6,
   "text": "But."
  },
  {
   "start": 793.4,
   "end": 793.92,
   "text": "And then I was."
  },
  {
   "start": 794.04,
   "end": 796.62,
   "text": "So I'm going to fill out this form called like the 383."
  },
  {
   "start": 796.62,
   "end": 797.08,
   "text": "Or whatever."
  },
  {
   "start": 797.2,
   "end": 797.76,
   "text": "To complain."
  },
  {
   "start": 798.88,
   "end": 799.2,
   "text": "But."
  },
  {
   "start": 799.2,
   "end": 801.76,
   "text": "Anyway that's the IRS for you."
  },
  {
   "start": 802.26,
   "end": 802.68,
   "text": "And so yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 802.76,
   "end": 803.36,
   "text": "Ever since then."
  },
  {
   "start": 803.4,
   "end": 804.66,
   "text": "Every year they're always sending me letters."
  },
  {
   "start": 805.14,
   "end": 806.0,
   "text": "Like I do my taxes."
  },
  {
   "start": 806.14,
   "end": 806.74,
   "text": "And then they send me a letter."
  },
  {
   "start": 807.08,
   "end": 809.1,
   "text": "And they send me a letter that was like really vague."
  },
  {
   "start": 809.28,
   "end": 809.56,
   "text": "They're like."
  },
  {
   "start": 809.6,
   "end": 810.6,
   "text": "You need the document."
  },
  {
   "start": 811.2,
   "end": 812.64,
   "text": "To be sent in by two weeks."
  },
  {
   "start": 812.96,
   "end": 813.78,
   "text": "Within two weeks."
  },
  {
   "start": 813.84,
   "end": 814.2,
   "text": "I was like."
  },
  {
   "start": 814.28,
   "end": 814.92,
   "text": "What document?"
  },
  {
   "start": 815.58,
   "end": 816.62,
   "text": "It was literally like that."
  },
  {
   "start": 816.66,
   "end": 817.56,
   "text": "Maybe I needed to call them."
  },
  {
   "start": 817.56,
   "end": 818.78,
   "text": "And ask them what document they wanted."
  },
  {
   "start": 819.94,
   "end": 820.18,
   "text": "But."
  },
  {
   "start": 820.18,
   "end": 823.04,
   "text": "Anyway I wasn't able to do any of that."
  },
  {
   "start": 823.16,
   "end": 824.34,
   "text": "I was too hooked on my website."
  },
  {
   "start": 827.44,
   "end": 827.8,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 828.64,
   "end": 831.58,
   "text": "If you're like one of these narcissistic virtue signers right now."
  },
  {
   "start": 831.66,
   "end": 832.52,
   "text": "Hate watching me and going."
  },
  {
   "start": 832.88,
   "end": 833.42,
   "text": "Well how can you?"
  },
  {
   "start": 833.48,
   "end": 833.86,
   "text": "You can't do that."
  },
  {
   "start": 833.94,
   "end": 834.16,
   "text": "Well."
  },
  {
   "start": 834.52,
   "end": 836.06,
   "text": "I also wasn't exercising."
  },
  {
   "start": 836.8,
   "end": 837.46,
   "text": "Which one's worse?"
  },
  {
   "start": 839.46,
   "end": 839.82,
   "text": "Anyways."
  },
  {
   "start": 841.82,
   "end": 842.18,
   "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
   "start": 842.28,
   "end": 842.7,
   "text": "Check it out."
  },
  {
   "start": 842.7,
   "end": 845.64,
   "text": "I've never seen two birds at the same time looking in the mirror."
  },
  {
   "start": 846.26,
   "end": 847.52,
   "text": "Usually it's just one."
  },
  {
   "start": 848.3,
   "end": 850.14,
   "text": "But now both of them are wanting to do it."
  },
  {
   "start": 850.8,
   "end": 850.98,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 851.0,
   "end": 852.88,
   "text": "I see them staring directly in that mirror."
  },
  {
   "start": 852.96,
   "end": 855.52,
   "text": "And look how filthy they made it by pecking at it."
  },
  {
   "start": 856.22,
   "end": 857.86,
   "text": "I need to go and clean that mirror."
  },
  {
   "start": 858.56,
   "end": 858.88,
   "text": "Anyway."
  },
  {
   "start": 864.52,
   "end": 864.92,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 865.06,
   "end": 866.6,
   "text": "So tomorrow I'm going to go."
  },
  {
   "start": 866.82,
   "end": 867.86,
   "text": "I'm going to ride to work."
  },
  {
   "start": 868.5,
   "end": 870.84,
   "text": "I'm going to come back and then clean."
  },
  {
   "start": 870.84,
   "end": 872.24,
   "text": "I think I'm going to clean the floor today."
  },
  {
   "start": 873.04,
   "end": 874.24,
   "text": "And then try to do taxes."
  },
  {
   "start": 875.14,
   "end": 877.1,
   "text": "And then definitely exercise tomorrow."
  },
  {
   "start": 877.28,
   "end": 877.82,
   "text": "Definitely exercise."
  },
  {
   "start": 877.9,
   "end": 878.82,
   "text": "In fact I would have today."
  },
  {
   "start": 878.82,
   "end": 881.66,
   "text": "And the only reason I didn't was because of these plants."
  },
  {
   "start": 881.78,
   "end": 882.44,
   "text": "I really needed."
  },
  {
   "start": 882.84,
   "end": 885.24,
   "text": "Want to make my house look spick and span."
  },
  {
   "start": 885.82,
   "end": 888.5,
   "text": "And now I have time to keep it that way."
  },
  {
   "start": 888.82,
   "end": 890.58,
   "text": "Because I'm not working on my website at home anymore."
  },
  {
   "start": 890.78,
   "end": 893.08,
   "text": "So I can like you know perfect it."
  },
  {
   "start": 893.18,
   "end": 894.74,
   "text": "And fix all the little things that."
  },
  {
   "start": 895.24,
   "end": 895.68,
   "text": "Because like."
  },
  {
   "start": 895.68,
   "end": 898.3,
   "text": "I put a lot of stuff on the wall."
  },
  {
   "start": 898.3,
